translations:
‘ein
			Auto herfuhr zor uns. Manchmal überholten wir es, (manchmal
			überholte es uns)’;

‘We (I) spent our (my) life in that manner until we (I) became
			fifteen years old (lit ‘until our (my) age became fifteen years
			old’)’ EL 5;

‘They
			brought him to a doctor, to Mardin. And from Mardin they moved him
			further to Diyarbakir’ EL 19;
